| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4322 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 956c481c-0878-5a62-89e3-a3ecf45ae6a8"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
